  "rationale": "Single sanctioned hero bookend, reused verbatim from the seeded project pattern hero-display-over-staggered-media. Only the MEDIA axis varies: the landscape hero-media now carries Web-gallery-1.jpg (the quieter gallery-interior backdrop) while the portrait overlap-media stays asset:null so the renderer's measured vase inset remains registered to the hero photo's lower-right edge, crossing it via media-over-media overlap + vertical stagger. Centered didone colossal title carries the sole gold accent on the inverse surface; eyebrow, support, and typographic arrow CTA are bound verbatim. novelty:adapt, seededFrom the seeded hero pattern \u2014 no other sections."
